00:17:57.760 --> 00:17:58.720
Lihat ke sini.

00:18:00.640 --> 00:18:02.280
Lihat ini.

00:18:04.240 --> 00:18:05.720
Menantu perempuanmu, Laxmi.

00:18:05.960 --> 00:18:07.800
